ulations. Because of its computational efficiency, the HSEED method allows\none to rapidly assess the ice nucleation ability of whole libraries of\ncrystalline substrates - a long-awaited computational development in e.g.\natmospheric science.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2018 21:29:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
