 hydrogenation step, or $\\leq$$0.02$ per H-atom induced\nreaction, assuming that H-atom addition and abstraction reactions equally\ncontribute to the overall reactive desorption fraction along the hydrogenation\nsequence. The astronomical relevance of this finding is discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Jun 2018 10:21:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-19"}
